       <div class="row intro">
        <div class="large-9 columns large-centered text-center">
         <h2>
          What is the Office of Environmental Health and Safety (EHS)?
         </h2>
         <p>
          EHS oversees University efforts to protect occupational health and the environment. EHS assists faculty and staff in maintaining safe, compliant workplaces.
         </p>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
